window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>He gave up the money.&nbsp;He gave up the power.&nbsp;Now all he has left is the law. </b></p> <p>Michael Brock is billing the hours, making the money, rushing relentlessly to the top of Drake &amp; Sweeney, a giant DC law firm.&nbsp;One step away from partnership, Michael has it all.&nbsp;Then, in an instant, it all comes undone.</p> <p>A homeless man takes nine lawyers hostage in the firm's plush offices.&nbsp;When it is all over, the man's blood is splattered on Michael's face - and suddenly Michael is willing to do the unthinkable.&nbsp;Rediscovering a conscience he lost long ago, Michael is leaving the big time for the streets where his attacker once lived - and where society's powerless need an advocate for justice.</p> <p>But there's one break Michael can't make: from a secret that has floated up from the depths of Drake &amp; Sweeney, from a confidential file that is now in Michael's hands, and from a conspiracy that has already taken lives.&nbsp;Now Michael's former partners are about to become his bitter enemies.&nbsp;Because to them, Michael Brock is the most dangerous man on the streets....&nbsp;</p>"; 
